          "order": 1,
          "title": "BARD CAN HELP YOU CODE",
          "summary": "Google’s language model Bard, when launched, refused to answer coding questions. That has changed now. It can help you code in a huge variety of languages and does a pretty good job! There hasn’t been any official validation released, so we don’t know how it compares to other program synthesis models, but it’s always nice to have options.",
