          "id": "tldr-ai:2023-04-24:o007",
          "order": 1,
          "title": "VOICE CLONING",
          "summary": "Transformers continue their march into all modalities, this time taking on audio with a cool voice cloning tool. There are some limitations, but with just a few seconds of audio, you can get a pretty great representation of your voice.",
          "url": "https://github.com/suno-ai/bark?utm_source=tldrai",
          "reading_time_minutes": null,
          "source_domain": "github.com",
          "content_type": "github_repo",
          "is_sponsor": false
        },
        {
          "id": "tldr-ai:2023-04-24:o008",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "LLAMA ACADEMY",
          "summary": "It seems like everywhere you look people are building retrieval augmentation into language models. Here is another tool to do that, using the almost-open sourced Llama models. This one has a nice recipe you can follow to teach the model about novel APIs and SDKs.",
          "url": "https://github.com/danielgross/LlamaAcademy?utm_source=tldrai",
          "reading_time_minutes": null,
          "source_domain": "github.com",
          "content_type": "github_repo",
          "is_sponsor": false
